
Privacy Policy for Code Cracker

This Privacy Policy describes how your personal information is collected, used, and shared when you use the Code Cracker mobile application (the "App").

Personal Information We Collect

When you use the App, we may collect certain information about you, including:

Device Information: We collect information about the device you use to access the App, including the device type, operating system, unique device identifiers, and mobile network information.

Usage Information: We collect information about how you use the App, such as the features you interact with, the content you view, and the actions you take.

Location Information: With your consent, we may collect information about your location using GPS, Wi-Fi, or other methods to provide location-based services within the App.

Contact Information: We may collect contact information you provide voluntarily, such as your email address, for purposes such as account registration or communication.

How We Use Your Personal Information

We use the personal information we collect to:

Provide and improve the App's functionality and user experience.
Respond to your inquiries, requests, and customer service needs.
Communicate with you about updates, news, and promotional offers related to the App.
Analyze usage trends and preferences to enhance the App's features and content.
Ensure the security and integrity of the App and our users.
Sharing Your Personal Information

We may share your personal information with third parties for the following purposes:

With service providers and business partners who assist us in operating the App and providing related services (e.g., hosting, analytics).
With your consent or at your direction, such as when you choose to share content from the App on social media platforms.
In response to legal requests, court orders, or legal processes, or to establish or exercise our legal rights or defend against legal claims.
In connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets, if the App is involved in a corporate transaction.
Your Choices

You can control certain types of personal information collected by the App through your device settings or by adjusting your preferences within the App. However, please note that disabling certain features may impact your ability to use the App fully.

Data Retention

We retain personal information collected through the App for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy, unless a longer retention period is required or permitted by law.

Children's Privacy

The App is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe that a child under 13 has provided personal information to us, please contact us immediately.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, please contact us at [contact email].
